    {
      "startFrame": 0,
      "endFrame": 6,
      "text": "Agents can now spend money and provision tools.",
      "stageId": "hero"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 0,
      "endFrame": 6,
      "text": "Here the mission is to resolve one hundred late-freight exceptions in seventy-two hours.",
      "stageId": "mission"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 6,
      "endFrame": 18,
      "text": "That is powerful, and dangerous.",
      "stageId": "hero"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 18,
      "endFrame": 24,
      "text": "Agent IC gives them a governed capital account.",
      "stageId": "hero"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 49,
      "endFrame": 98,
      "text": "Hermes and Nemotron load the intake skill, normalize the proposal, and score viability.",
      "stageId": "mission"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 98,
      "endFrame": 178,
      "text": "OpenShell creates a sandbox around the agent, scopes the network policy, and records the invariants.",
      "stageId": "sandbox"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 178,
      "endFrame": 221,
      "text": "OpenShell intercepts the call and returns four-oh-three Forbidden.",
      "stageId": "sandbox"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 221,
      "endFrame": 248,
      "text": "No session, no money moves.",
      "stageId": "sandbox"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 248,
      "endFrame": 323,
      "text": "Stripe records a bounded one-hundred-dollar authorization.",
      "stageId": "stripe"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 323,
      "endFrame": 398,
      "text": "The Stripe Link skill can buy a fifteen-dollar SaaS subscription with a one-time card, but only after human approval.",
      "stageId": "stripeSkill"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 398,
      "endFrame": 482,
      "text": "The agent tries to buy a one-hundred-fifty-dollar premium lookup API.",
      "stageId": "blocked"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 482,
      "endFrame": 580,
      "text": "Then the agent imports evidence: one hundred cases processed, forty-eight auto-triaged, ninety-one percent QA agreement.",
      "stageId": "evidence"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 580,
      "endFrame": 660,
      "text": "Within the remaining envelope, Hermes skills auto-order replacement parts and notify the team in Slack.",
      "stageId": "skills"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 660,
      "endFrame": 1222,
      "text": "The decision is continue, with a two-hundred-fifty-dollar next cap and draft-only autonomy.",
      "stageId": "decision"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 1222,
      "endFrame": 1644,
      "text": "Hermes saves the whole procedure as a reusable playbook.",
      "stageId": "decision"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 1644,
      "endFrame": 2053,
      "text": "Lower the QA threshold to eighty-two percent, and the decision flips to kill.",
      "stageId": "counterfactual"
    },
    {
      "startFrame": 2053,
      "endFrame": 2436,
      "text": "This is how enterprises let agents operate with money without losing control.",
      "stageId": "counterfactual"
    }
  ],
